{"tid":1148030,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"咁樣即係有定冇offer？我分唔清楚","createTime":"2019-05-10T08:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T06:20:36.000Z","uid":82672,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"96cfe303b3e19bd66c7dc383d220a59ee2cc0479","tid":1148030,"uid":82672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:02:02.000Z","msg":"我喺4月尾in左份工，話要等2星期到先有result<br />\n因為約interview嘅時候知道interviewer上個星期放假，而佢地喺呢個星期重要再見其他candidate<br />\n咁我就keep住等啦<br />\n到今日我收到其他公司offer，但係我又想做呢間公司多啲，<br />\n所以我就打俾個負責hr問下係咪出左offer俾其他人，都星期5我都打定輸數<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />hr<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> halo，我想問下個post你地係咪已經出左offer喇，因為上次嚟interview話會兩星期<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你嘅意思係你？定其他人？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他人？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喔，重未阿<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁嘅意思我係咪落選左？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你係幾時in架？(4月尾) 喔，咁嘅話你機會都微啲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁嘅意思即係代表我落選左？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩個星期嘅話都係架啦？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為上次arrange interview個陣你話上星期interivewer唔得閒，所以今個星期先會再in人，然後話2個星期到先有消息，而因為我收到其他公司offer，但都對你地公司有興趣，所以想問問confirm<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為佢地有適合人選會俾我地make offer，但係我地重未收到。而佢地啱啱in完呢一batch會再in，所以我諗你機會都微。不過佢地俾左啲唔啱嘅candidate我，你叫咩名？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />xxx，唔該曬你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係又冇印象有你份野喎&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &hellip;咁阿，或者你介唔介意幫我問一問？因為我對你地公司的確有興趣啲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> errrr，因為佢地有合適人選就俾我地make offer，blah blah blah&hellip; 不過如果你下星期都冇消息嘅話，就應該冇架喇。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁嘅話&hellip;好啦，唔該曬你先<br />\n<br />\n利申：我打定左輸數，但係個hr咁講我都分唔到佢係咪婉轉咁refuse我，但係字裡行間又俾到啲希望我<br />\n<br />\n但其實本來係in manager+ senior<br />\n但因為我in evening time，所以得senior in我<br />\n會唔會係因為manager冇份in 所以hold起左我先？<br />\n我唔知咁關唔關事<br />\n媽阿，下星期又要覆返另一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1924bdc99d54136b92b64b0d8400606353131a40","tid":1148030,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:06:43.000Z","msg":"無關係架<br />\n做一日辭職都得啦"},{"pid":"8c9005bf11fef097c288bacfdf8a92b9adc48e65","tid":1148030,"uid":92233,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:15:25.000Z","msg":"驚咩ACCEPT住先 簽完約未返工都可以REJECT"},{"pid":"16744aa552d3925e3561d6b19cbe8d5e5da9237d","tid":1148030,"uid":92233,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8c9005bf11fef097c288bacfdf8a92b9adc48e65","tid":1148030,"uid":92233,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:15:25.000Z","msg":"驚咩ACCEPT住先 簽完約未返工都可以REJECT"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:15:38.000Z","msg":"咪*"},{"pid":"f3ebe99ae908f93503cfde4ef5681d9f9f35ed81","tid":1148030,"uid":213014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:28:36.000Z","msg":"咪接左有offer個間先，到你有興趣個間真係比offer先決定轉唔轉啦"},{"pid":"fbc512aa1440cdb255b24a12ec39b09df71294df","tid":1148030,"uid":82672,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1924bdc99d54136b92b64b0d8400606353131a40","tid":1148030,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:06:43.000Z","msg":"無關係架<br />\n做一日辭職都得啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:34:18.000Z","msg":"返左工無耐就辭會唔會臭朵㗎？<br />\n因為都大間機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br /